Great service and great food

GREAT CUSTOMER SERVICE! Authentic Mexican Food! The nachos are delicious! The sopes are super delicious and they added nopales, a few potatoes and jalapeños in a little wrapped aluminum foil! I think they were grilled but it was tasty on top of my meatless sopes! The jugo de Jamaica is very delicious!!!!! I ordered horchata before with no ice and I didn’t like it as much! But over all great over the phone service to place an order for delivery! The delivery guys ROCK!!!! They bike their way to your location with a huge smile and respectful! I always leave a great TIP!  I’ve ordered about 6 times so far for lunch break! I def need to visit this restaurant! Love eating authentic Mexican food reminds me of back home! Thank you all for the great service and the cooks are amazing!!!!! Y’all won’t regret eating their delicious food!!!!!! 🇲🇽
